### Properties used by jEdit

plugin.HelloWorldPlugin.name=Hello World!
plugin.HelloWorldPlugin.author=Slava Pestov
plugin.HelloWorldPlugin.version=2.0
plugin.HelloWorldPlugin.docs=HelloWorld.html

### These tell jEdit what JDK and jEdit version we require

## We require jEdit 2.7pre2, because that is the version which
## introduced the new action API
plugin.HelloWorldPlugin.depend.0=jedit 02.07.02.00

## If your plugin uses JDK 1.2 specific stuff, uncomment the next line.
#plugin.HelloWorldPlugin.depend.1=jdk 1.2

# The menu item label
hello-world.label=Hello World

### Properties for use by this plugin

# Strings used by the 'Hello World' dialog box
hello-world.title=Hello World
hello-world.message=Hello world! jEdit is a cool editor!
